<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1922-05-16T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1922-05-16T13:00:00-05:00" n="381" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d381">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">824.51/105: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Bolivia</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Cottrell</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-05-16T14:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">May 16,
                                        1922—2 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>7. Your 15, May 2, 3 p.m.</p>
                        <p>Attorneys for American bankers report their proposition accepted by
                            Bolivian representatives. Please keep Department advised of progress
                            briefly by cable.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>